title: Maxine Gross 2017 Interview Transcript
description: This is the transcript of the interview between Mehrnoosh Mohammadian, Sydney Parker, and Maxine Gross. This interview was conducted on November 17, 2017 and discusses Gross' experience as an undergraduate theater student at the University of Maryland, graduating in 1981.
